==English==

===Phrasal Verb===
''to'' '''get away'''
# To avoid [[capture]] and [[escape]]
#: ''Surround the bank! Don't let the robber '''get away'''!''
#: ''I almost caught the critter, but it '''got away''' from me.''

====Usage note====
*If used with an object, use the preposition ''from'', as in the second example.

